<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><entry xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="entry_fælvaryn" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>fælvaryn</orth><form type="inflected" subtype="ptcp"><orth>fælværd</orth></form></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>fælvarun</orth><form type="inflected" subtype="ptcp"><orth>fælvard</orth></form></form><sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>пробовать</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>try</q></cit></sense><sense><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>испытывать</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>test</q></cit></sense></sense><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_fælvaryn." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>bafælvarūt ma he ūcy xorz mīnīwæg</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>испытайте-ка это хорошее свойство</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>try this good feature</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>102</biblScope></bibl></cit><cit type="example"><quote>dæ cirq... yscyrǧ kæn æmæ jæ bafælvar mæ bærzæjyl</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>наточи свой меч и испытай его на моей шее</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>sharpen your sword and test it on my neck</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Нарт._сказ."/><biblScope>87</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><cit type="exampleGroup" corresp="#sense_." n=""><cit type="example"><quote>bafælvarūt ma he ūcy xorz mīnīwæg</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>испытайте-ка это хорошее свойство</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>try this good feature</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Коста"/><biblScope>102</biblScope></bibl></cit><cit type="example"><quote>dæ cirq... yscyrǧ kæn æmæ jæ bafælvar mæ bærzæjyl</quote><cit type="translation" xml:lang="ru"><q>наточи свой меч и испытай его на моей шее</q></cit><cit type="translation" xml:lang="en"><q>sharpen your sword and test it on my neck</q></cit><bibl><ref target="#src_Нарт._сказ."/><biblScope>87</biblScope></bibl></cit></cit><etym xml:lang="ru">Из %ifæl-war-%i ← <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*pari-var-</w></mentioned>. Ср. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>var-</w><gloss><q>выбирать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>var-</w><gloss><q>выбирать (для себя)</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/><gloss><q>предпочитать</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="cu"><lang/><w>велѣти, волꙗ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="got"><lang/><w>waljan</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/><w>wählen</w><gloss><q>выбирать</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="de"><w>wollen</w><gloss><q>хотеть</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/><w>volo</w><gloss><q>хочу</q></gloss></mentioned> и пр. Глагол %ivar-%i означал также (например в ведийском) <mentioned xml:lang="sa-vaidika"><lang/><w/><gloss><q>предоставлять</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa-vaidika"><w/><gloss><q>доставлять</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa-vaidika"><w/><gloss><q>давать</q></gloss></mentioned>, . Это значение удержалось в <xr><ref target="#entry_waryn"/></xr> | %ii-warun%i ‘распределять’, ‘делить’. Ср. также <xr><ref target="#entry_ævzaryn"/></xr> ‘выбирать’ и <xr><ref target="#entry_bar"/></xr> ‘воля’, ‘право’.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From %ifæl-war-%i ← <mentioned xml:lang="ira"><lang/><w>*pari-var-</w></mentioned>. Cf. <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/><w>var-</w><gloss><q>choose</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/><w>var-</w><gloss><q>choose (for oneself)</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/><gloss><q>prefer</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="cu"><lang/><w>велѣти, волꙗ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="got"><lang/><w>waljan</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/><w>wählen</w><gloss><q>choose</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="de"><w>wollen</w><gloss><q>want</q></gloss></mentioned>, , <mentioned xml:lang="la"><lang/><w>volo</w><gloss><q>I want</q></gloss></mentioned> etc. The verb %ivar-%i also meant (e.g., in Vedic) <mentioned xml:lang="sa-vaidika"><lang/><w/><gloss><q>give</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa-vaidika"><w/><gloss><q>deliver</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sa-vaidika"><w/><gloss><q>yield</q></gloss></mentioned>, . This meaning is present in <xr><ref target="#entry_waryn"/></xr> | %ii-warun%i ‘distribute’, ‘share’. Cf. also <xr><ref target="#entry_ævzaryn"/></xr> ‘choose’ and <xr><ref target="#entry_bar"/></xr> ‘will’, ‘right’.</etym></entry>